'''''Kingin' with Tyga''''' is an American [[reality television]] series that premiered on July 24, 2015, on [[MTV2]]. The show was announced on April 14, 2015. The six episode, half-hour series follows the life of rapper [[Tyga]] as he works on his music career and chronicles his luxurious lifestyle.<ref name=THR>{{cite web|first=Lesley|last=Goldberg|title='Celebrity Deathmatch' Revived at MTV2 (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/celebrity-deathmatch-revived-at-mtv2-788551|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|date=April 14, 2015|accessdate=July 19, 2015}}</ref><ref name=MTV>{{cite web|title=About ''Kingin' with Tyga''|url=http://www.mtv.com/shows/kingin-with-tyga/|publisher=MTV|accessdate=July 19, 2015}}</ref> The show returned with a second season which premiered August 4, 2016 on [[MTV]].

